   "source": "<ROUTINE CLOSED? (WLOC VISIBLE?)\n  <COND (<AND <T? .WLOC>\n\t      <MC-ISNOT? .WLOC ,FL-OPENED>\n\t      <OR <NOT .VISIBLE?>\n\t\t  <MC-ISNOT? .WLOC ,FL-TRANSPARENT>>\n\t      <MC-ISNOT? .WLOC ,FL-SURFACE>\n\t      <MC-ISNOT? .WLOC ,FL-ALIVE>\n\t      <NOT <IN? .WLOC ,ROOMS>>>\n\t T)>>"
