   "source": "<ROUTINE V-LAND ()\n\t<DEBUGGING? <RT-DEBUG-VERB \"V-LAND\">>\n\t<COND (<MC-PRSO? ,ROOMS>\n\t       <COND (<IN? ,CH-PLAYER ,TH-BOAT>\n\t\t      <RT-LAND-BOAT>)\n\t\t     (T\n\t\t      <TELL \"Very good. Next week, we'll learn the word for\nwater.\" CR>)>\n\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t      (<MC-PRSO? ,TH-BOAT>\n\t       <COND (<IN? ,CH-PLAYER ,TH-BOAT>\n\t\t      <RT-LAND-BOAT>)\n\t\t     (T\n\t\t      <TELL ,K-MUST-BE-IN-BOAT-MSG \"land it.\" CR>)>)\n\t      (T\n\t       <TELL \"You can't land \" THEO \"!\" CR>)>\n\t<RTRUE>>"
