   "source": "<ROUTINE RT-QSR (\"AUX\" KEY)\n\t<IFSOUND <KILL-SOUNDS>>\n\t<TELL \"The game is no longer afoot.\" CR CR>\n\t<REPEAT ()\n\t\t<TELL \"Do you wish to: (1) Quit, (2) Restart, (3) Restore, (4) Hints\">\n\t\t<COND (<MC-T? ,GL-CAN-UNDO>\n\t\t       <TELL \", (5) Undo\">)>\n\t\t<TELL \" ?\" CR>\n\t\t<SET KEY <INPUT 1>>\n\t\t<COND (<EQUAL? .KEY 49>\n\t\t       <QUIT>\n\t\t       <TELL \"Quit failed.\" CR>)\n\t\t      (<EQUAL? .KEY 50>\n\t\t       <RESTART>\n\t\t       <TELL \"Restart failed.\" CR>)\n\t\t      (<EQUAL? .KEY 51>\n\t\t       <COND (<MC-T? ,GL-DEBUG-FLAG>\n\t\t\t      <V-REFRESH>)>\n\t\t       <RT-P-CLEAR>\n\t\t       <PUTB ,GL-OOPS-INBUF 1 0>\n\t\t       <RESTORE>\n\t\t       <TELL \"Restore failed.\" CR>)\n\t\t      (<EQUAL? .KEY 52>\n\t\t       <V-HINT>\n\t\t       <V-REFRESH>\n\t\t       <AGAIN>)\n\t\t      (<AND <EQUAL? .KEY 53>\n\t\t\t    <MC-T? ,GL-CAN-UNDO>>\n\t\t       <V-UNDO>)>>>"
